	‚Ä¢	9:30 PM - 5:30 AM: Sleep (8 hours)
Study Techniques to Use:
The Golden 4 Techniques:
	1.	Active Recall: Cover your notes and write everything you remember, then check
	2.	Spaced Repetition: Review the same topics on different days
	3.	Pomodoro Method: 25 minutes focus + 5 minutes break
	4.	Teaching Method: Explain concepts out loud as if teaching someone
Subject-Specific Techniques:

