Critical Success Tips:
During Study Sessions:
	1.	Phone OFF or in another room - no distractions!
	2.	Drink water - keep a bottle with you
	3.	Take breaks seriously - walk, stretch, pray
	4.	Don‚Äôt just read - actively DO (write, draw, solve)
	5.	Practice with TIME LIMITS - simulate exam conditions
For Each Subject:
	‚Ä¢	Always START with active recall (what do I remember?)
	‚Ä¢	Then CHECK your notes (what did I miss?)
	‚Ä¢	Then PRACTICE (solve problems/write answers)
	‚Ä¢	Then REVIEW again the next day (spaced repetition!)
Avoid These Study Mistakes:
	‚Ä¢	‚ùå Just reading notes over and over
	‚Ä¢	‚ùå Highlighting everything
	‚Ä¢	‚ùå Studying with your phone nearby
	‚Ä¢	‚ùå Cramming one subject for hours without breaks
	‚Ä¢	‚ùå Not testing yourself
