	‚Ä¢	Best focus hours: Right after Fajr (5:30-9:00 AM) - tackle hardest subjects!
	‚Ä¢	Mid-morning: Good for practice problems (9:00-11:30 AM)
	‚Ä¢	Before lunch: Review and consolidation (11:30 AM-1:30 PM)
